---
title: TDD Workflow
description: Red-Green-Refactor TDD cycle for Hospeda development
author: Tech Team
date: 2025-11-06
---

```mermaid
graph LR
    %% Red Phase
    Start([🎯 Start New Feature])
    WriteTest[✍️ Write Test<br/>test/feature.test.ts]
    AAA[📋 AAA Pattern<br/>Arrange<br/>Act<br/>Assert]
    RunRed[▶️ Run Test]
    TestFails{❌ Test Fails?}

    %% Green Phase
    WriteCode[💻 Write Minimal Code<br/>src/feature.ts]
    RunGreen[▶️ Run Test Again]
    TestPasses{✅ Test Passes?}

    %% Refactor Phase
    NeedsRefactor{🤔 Needs<br/>Refactoring?}
    Refactor[♻️ Refactor Code<br/>- Extract functions<br/>- Remove duplication<br/>- Improve naming]
    RunRefactor[▶️ Run Test Again]
    StillPasses{✅ Still Passes?}

    %% Quality Check
    Coverage{📊 90% Coverage<br/>Achieved?}
    TypeCheck[🔍 Type Check<br/>pnpm typecheck]
    Lint[🧹 Lint<br/>pnpm lint]
    AllGood{✅ All Checks<br/>Pass?}

    %% Commit
    Commit[💾 Commit Changes<br/>feat: add feature]
    Push[⬆️ Push to GitHub]

    %% Next Feature
    MoreFeatures{🔄 More Features?}
    Done([✨ Done])

    %% Flow
    Start --> WriteTest
    WriteTest --> AAA
    AAA --> RunRed
    RunRed --> TestFails

    TestFails -->|Yes ✓| WriteCode
    TestFails -->|No ✗<br/>Test should fail first| WriteTest

    WriteCode --> RunGreen
    RunGreen --> TestPasses

    TestPasses -->|No ✗<br/>Fix code| WriteCode
    TestPasses -->|Yes ✓| NeedsRefactor

    NeedsRefactor -->|Yes| Refactor
    NeedsRefactor -->|No| Coverage

    Refactor --> RunRefactor
    RunRefactor --> StillPasses

    StillPasses -->|No ✗<br/>Revert refactor| NeedsRefactor
    StillPasses -->|Yes ✓| Coverage

    Coverage -->|No ✗<br/>Write more tests| WriteTest
    Coverage -->|Yes ✓| TypeCheck

    TypeCheck --> Lint
    Lint --> AllGood

    AllGood -->|No ✗<br/>Fix issues| WriteCode
    AllGood -->|Yes ✓| Commit

    Commit --> Push
    Push --> MoreFeatures

    MoreFeatures -->|Yes| Start
    MoreFeatures -->|No| Done

    %% Styling
    classDef redPhase fill:#ef4444,stroke:#dc2626,color:#fff
    classDef greenPhase fill:#10b981,stroke:#059669,color:#fff
    classDef refactorPhase fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#d97706,color:#fff
    classDef qualityPhase fill:#8b5cf6,stroke:#7c3aed,color:#fff
    classDef commitPhase fill:#06b6d4,stroke:#0891b2,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#6b7280,stroke:#4b5563,color:#fff

    class WriteTest,AAA,RunRed,TestFails redPhase
    class WriteCode,RunGreen,TestPasses greenPhase
    class NeedsRefactor,Refactor,RunRefactor,StillPasses refactorPhase
    class Coverage,TypeCheck,Lint,AllGood qualityPhase
    class Commit,Push commitPhase
    class TestFails,TestPasses,NeedsRefactor,StillPasses,Coverage,AllGood,MoreFeatures decision
```
